entries.femaleVariant: You're not going to that whore of yours out in the Badlands! No way!
Hon, you don't even know her. Never saw her. How d'you know she's a whore?
Those sandeating sluts are all the same.
Aaah, you mean Jolie... But she worked in a bakery. Jill's a ripper. Nothing to do with each other.
Look, she'll adjust my joints, half-price.
Fine, go! Just make sure you take all your shit with you, 'cause you won't be coming back here! What do you even see in her?
Ehhh, nothing. She's not even pretty... sure got less of a mouth on her, though.
